            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Tanya? I didn't think I'd meet you here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I know. I'm gonna go sell salt to a merchant."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I see, so you do deliveries, too.<CR>You're such a good girl."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "But isn't salt really heavy? Are you gonna be okay by yourself?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x185,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Umm, I'm used to it, so it doesn't seem that heavy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x187,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I've got some on me right now,<CR>but it's not that heavy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Then that must mean your salt is freshly gathered."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, I don't think it makes any<CR>difference how \"freshly gathered\"<CR>the salt is."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "That's not true. It has a better feel when it's freshly gathered."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I'd be really happy if you could share some with me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x45,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Haha, sure. Gimme a second."
